      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Christian Daley</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/File:ChristianRDaley.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/8/8d/ChristianRDaley.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:ChristianRDaley.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Christian Daley  <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Christian R. Daley</b>,<br />\nan American computer scientist and software engineer, M.Sc. in CS from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_California,_Santa_Barbara\">UC Santa Barbara</a> in 2019 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\nHe is author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engines</a> <a href=\"/JFresh\" title=\"JFresh\">JFresh</a> and its successor <a href=\"/Spartan\" title=\"Spartan\">Spartan</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2013\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2013</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2014_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2014 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_Daley&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2013\">2013</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_Daley&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2013\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2210\">Null Move Fail</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 10, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2212\">Quiescence Search and Checkmates</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 11, 2013 &#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a>, <a href=\"/Checkmate\" title=\"Checkmate\">Checkmate</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2214\">Transposition Tables</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 12, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2218\">Implementing pvs</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 13, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">PVS</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2220\">Fail High nodes</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 14, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">Fail-High</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2221\">UCI Programming</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 15, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2225\">Exact node values</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 16, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Exact_Score\" title=\"Exact Score\">Exact Score</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2228\">Extracting moves from bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 18, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Bitboard_Serialization\" title=\"Bitboard Serialization\">Bitboard Serialization</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2238\">Perft and Captures</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 24, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a>, <a href=\"/Captures\" title=\"Captures\">Captures</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2240\">Occupancy Variations</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 25, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2245\">UCI protocol not working</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 27, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2250\">Make and Unmake implementation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, February 01, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Make_Move\" title=\"Make Move\">Make Move</a>, <a href=\"/Unmake_Move\" title=\"Unmake Move\">Unmake Move</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2554\">Saving info before making a move</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, December 30, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Make_Move\" title=\"Make Move\">Make Move</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2014_...\">2014 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_Daley&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2014 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2585\">Internal Iterative Deepening Payoffs</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, February 01, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=2973\">New UCI engine: Spartan</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">CDaley11</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, April 23, 2016</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_Daley&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/christiandaley/\">Christian R. Daley | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/christiandaley\">christiandaley (Christian Daley) · GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_Daley&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=